list.abstract: 《迷糊餐厅》（WORKING!!）是由A-1 Pictures制作，平池芳正、德本善信等执导，福山润、阿澄佳奈、藤田咲、喜多村英梨、渡边久美子等担任主要配音的13集日本动画，于2010年4月4日在日本TOKYO MX首播，中国内地于2010年4月4日在bilibili发布。 动画改编自高津雁野创作同名杂志漫画，讲述了小鸟游机缘巧合下来到瓦古娜利亚餐厅打工，发现餐厅店员怪异却有趣，也渐渐融入到了别具特色的餐厅打工生活中的故事。

yingyinNormal.en: He's always working. No, he's not always working, Lily.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他只顾着工作不，他...他并没有只顾着工作啊，莉莉。

yingyinNormal.en: Mummy Pig is working on her computer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 猪妈妈在电脑前工作。

yingyinNormal.en: Mummy Pig is working on her computer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 猪妈妈在电脑前工作。

yingyinNormal.en: Mummy Pig is working on her computer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 猪妈妈正在电脑上工作。

yingyinNormal.en: Have you thought about working here?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你有没有想过在这儿工作？

yingyinNormal.en: So is it horrible? Is everybody working really hard?
yingyinNormal.zh: 很难受吗？每个人都在认真工作吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Don't mess with me. What, you're working with Robertson?
yingyinNormal.zh: 别耍我，你跟罗伯森一起工作？

yingyinNormal.en: The hardest working person in the country is Miss Rabbit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个国家工作最努力的人就是兔子小姐。

yingyinNormal.en: The hardest working person in the country is Miss Rabbit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个国家工作最努力的人就是兔子小姐。

yingyinNormal.en: I can't believe I'm working for a corporate coffee place.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也不敢相信自己沦落到在连锁咖啡店工作。

yingyinNormal.en: Mommy Pig is working on the computer. Mommy. Hello Peppa.
yingyinNormal.zh: 猪妈妈正在电脑上工作。妈妈。你好，佩奇。

yingyinNormal.en: What? What is not working? Me not working isn't working. So go back to work.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么？什么不行？我不工作是不行的。那就回去工作呗。

yingyinNormal.en: Why aren't you working?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你怎么没在工作？

yingyinNormal.en: Have you had a busy day? Yes, I've been working very hard. We've been working very hard too. We've been shopkeepers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你今天工作忙不忙呀？忙啊，我今天工作非常努力。我们今天也在非常努力的工作哦。我们两个当了商店的老板。

yingyinNormal.en: Two minutes people. Mia, you're coming, right? I can't! I'm working. What? Did she just say Working?
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有两分钟宝贝儿们，米娅你也来，对吗？不行！我要工作。什么？她刚才是不是说工作？

yingyinNormal.en: Daddy, have you had a busy day? Yes, I've been working very hard. We've been working very hard too. We've been shopkeepers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 爸爸，你今天工作忙不忙呀？忙啊，我今天工作非常努力。我们今天也在非常努力的工作哦。我们两个当了商店的老板。

yingyinNormal.en: I heard there were jobs. Go on. I was working at Siemens when I heard the SS was recruiting.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我听说那儿有工作。继续。我在西门子工作时听说党卫军在招聘。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey. Oh, how was your first day working at the restaurant? Damn.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第一天在餐厅工作的情况如何？可恶。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, that'd be much worse than being 28, and still working here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对，那要比28岁还在这里工作惨多了。

yingyinNormal.en: For your information, Emily is working tonight. Yeah, one would assume, on getting out of the pit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 跟你报告一下，艾米丽，今晚要工作有人会认为她的工作就是要爬出那个深坑。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: 20 percent of Americans who have been unemployed for at least a year report having depression, double the rate for <highlight>working</highlight> Americans.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 失业至少一年的美国人中有20%称患有抑郁症，这一比例是美国工薪阶层的两倍。

examination_example.sentence: The family's poverty forced Dickens to work in a shoe-polish factory, where the other <highlight>working</highlight> boys mocked him as "the young gentleman."
examination_example.sentence_trans: 家庭的贫困迫使狄更斯在一家鞋油厂工作，其他在那里工作的男孩嘲笑他为“年轻的绅士”。

examination_example.sentence: His biographies were held up as beacons to guide the <highlight>working</highlight> man through his difficult life.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他的传记被奉为指路明灯，指引这位工人度过他艰难的一生。

examination_example.sentence: There is a gap in <highlight>working</highlight>-class jobs, but the workers who need those jobs most aren't equipped to do them.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 工人阶级的工作岗位中存在缺口，但最需要这些工作的工人却没有能力去做。

examination_example.sentence: At a time when the <highlight>working</highlight> class has turned the country on its political head, one solution is staring us in the face.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在一个工人阶级改变了国家政治面貌的时代，一个解决方案就摆在我们面前。

examination_example.sentence: Joe Blow, Joe Palooka, Joe Magrac...a <highlight>working</highlight> class name.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Joe Blow，Joe Palooka，Joe Magrac…一个工人阶级的名字。

examination_example.sentence: Creating an ideal <highlight>working</highlight> environment will make it easier for them to get down to their assignments quickly.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 创造一个理想的工作环境会使他们更容易地迅速开始工作。

examination_example.sentence: Employers' gain from remote <highlight>working</highlight> should go to employees as compensation.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 雇主从远程工作中获得的收益应该作为补偿给雇员。

examination_example.sentence: First, we are <highlight>working</highlight> to replicate (复制) these findings in more diverse school communities.

examination_example.sentence: Children of educated and upper-middle-class parents turn out to be far more curious than children of <highlight>working</highlight> class.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 受过良好教育的中上层家庭的孩子比工人阶级的孩子更有好奇心。

数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。
